Video Game Command Architecture
│
├── Strategic Layer (Game Mastery & AI Director)
│   ├── Game Objective Management
│   ├── Dynamic Scenario Generation
│   ├── Player Progression Systems
│   └── AI Director (Pacing & Challenge Scaling)
│
├── Operational Layer (Game Systems Coordination)
│   ├── Mission/Quest Control Engine
│   ├── Faction/Team Behavior Systems
│   ├── Resource & Economy Management
│   └── Environmental Control (Weather, Terrain, Events)
│
├── Tactical Layer (Unit & Agent Control)
│   ├── AI Behavior Trees / Decision Trees
│   │   ├── Patrol / Guard / Search
│   │   └── Attack / Defend / Flee
│   ├── Player Input Interpreter
│   └── NPC State Management
│
└── Execution Layer (System Interfaces & Feedback)
    ├── Animation & Physics Engine
    ├── Audio/Visual Feedback System
    ├── Collision Detection
    └── Network Synchronization (for multiplayer)
